{"id":"1700","name":"Amazon Price Tracker - Penny Parrot","tagline":"Enables you to look up the price history of an Amazon product from an amazon.com product page.","icon":"ios12 c4292093695 g59828","latest":"4696","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4>Penny Parrot - Amazon Price Tracker</h4>\n<hr>\n<p>This shortcut helps you quickly view the price history of a product on amazon.com. Unfortunately, it only works for amazon.com at this time. We are planning on supporting other Amazon locales in the future.</p>\n<h6>This shortcut can be used in two different ways:</h6>\n<ol>\n<li>From an amazon.com product page in Chrome or Safari, then tap Share -&gt; Penny Parrot and an easily dismissable window will pop up to view history and create a price alert.</li>\n<li>Searching by product name. Highlight some text, tap Share -&gt; Penny Parrot and find the relevant result to view price history on Amazon.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>There is a guide and video available on how to set it up on the <a href=\"https://pennyparrot.com/blog/ios-shortcuts-for-iphone\">Penny Parrot blog</a>.</p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.0 - Jan. 22, 2019, 1:47 a.m.</strong></p>"}